sources.title: Go-Get-'Em, Haines (1936) CRIME-ADVENTURE
sources.description:
Stars: William Boyd, Sheila Terry, Eleanor Hunt 
Director: Sam Newfield

A reporter on the trail of a business tycoon, follows his subject onto an ocean liner and gets wound up in a cruise full of intrigue, romance and murder!
